    <p>
      Kp is calculated from <strong>13 magnetometer stations</strong> located across the globe at mid-latitudes. These stations measure tiny fluctuations in Earth's magnetic field every 3 hours.
    </p>

    <h3>The K-Index System</h3>
    <ol>
